# Marlin Processor Overview

This page lists all Marlin processors available in the Key4hep software stack,
collected from the active environment. Use the search box to filter by processor
name. Click a processor name to reveal its parameters.

Total: **{{ total_algorithms }} processors**.

```{raw} html
<style>
#processor-overview {
  margin: 1em 0;
}
#processor-overview .proc-filter-bar {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1em;
  margin-bottom: 1em;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
#processor-overview #proc-search {
  flex: 1;
  min-width: 220px;
  padding: 0.4em 0.6em;
